      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEST ON MODEL (4) is a talented type who notched her 14th career success when too good (30.02) at this track last time. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Well placed and will be tough to beat. RIPPIN' BLUE (7) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 4 lengths into second (30.30) at this track in a Grade 5 over 520m. Leading chance. CYCLONE CALYPSO (6) started big odds in tougher last time when finishing 4th over 520m at this track. Was a this track winner in lesser company the start prior. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Can do much better this time. HARD TO FORGET (1) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
